253
00:13:44,799 --> 00:13:46,120
I won't give up so easily.

254
00:13:54,159 --> 00:13:55,320
Dr. Xiao.

255
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,639
What's so good about Bai Zhu?

256
00:13:57,679 --> 00:13:59,200
