00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:45,440
But as a doctor,

447
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:47,960
our priority is the patient's condition.

448
00:21:50,799 --> 00:21:51,960
I knew about the shadow in my liver...

449
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:54,799
